name: MISA
description:
Mix of
Impressive
SD
Art models

MISA. A powerful wide range model based on Waifu Diffusion 1.5 Beta 2 Aesthetic, Quattro4Merge+i, and Illuminati V1.1.

The most interesting thing about this model is that it is pretty good at generating half Asian half European beauties.

The biggest improvement is that we no longer need long negative prompts. In most cases, it will work fine with just a couple of triggered negative tags.
